Description: Your are bidding on a 2014 Gibson Les Paul Studio Pro Deluxe in Tobacco Burst Candy with Original Brown case. It is in excellent condition. It has slight buckle rash in the back, ( nothing through the finish), 1 very small ding on the front about an eighth of an inch long, not very visible unless you are looking for it, and a small ding on the upper side, again not very visible.Beautiful Flame top. FINISHED WITH ULTRA-HIGH GLOSS LACQUER Neck is straight, frets are like new. Plays like butter. Electronics all work perfectly. Pickups sound amazing.Black plastic parts were all switched out for the beige colored Gibson parts, and Gold vintage style knobs. The Jack plate has a small crack in the corner. Everything else is in perfect shape.The case shows a little bit of wear from the 10 or so gigs it did. No rips or tears.Overall I would compare this to a standard. just without the binding. For a lot less money.Only selling to fund another Gibson. Some Specs from the Gibson Website: ‘57 CLASSIC AND BURSTBUCKER PRO PICKUPS ENHANCE THE PAF LEGEND WITH PUSH-PULL TUNED COIL TAPS THE SATISFYING SUBSTANCE OF MAHOGANY, WITH MODERN WEIGHT RELIEF FOR MAX COMFORT DEPEND ON THE EXTREME TUNING STABILITY OF GROVER “KIDNEY” TUNERS AND TUNE-O-MATIC BRIDGE ‘60S SLIM TAPER MAHOGANY NECK WITH COMPOUND RADIUS FINGERBOARD DELIVERS WICKED FAST ACTION More info here. http://www.gibson.com/products/electric-guitars/2014/les-paul-studiopro.aspx
